"kind":"text","text":"meaning as expl. below; (JK, S, K;) in any of its senses: (TA:) said of a young bird, (JK, S, A, Msb,) meaning [as above, or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zagab","text_ar":"زَغَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"down"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grew forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its feathers were small:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and, said of a boy, or a young child,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zagab","text_ar":"زَغَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"downy hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grew forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aizolagab~a","text_ar":"اِزْلَغَبَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also said of a young bird [in the same sense as the verbs above: (see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zlgb","text_ar":"زلغب"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or] as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its feathers came forth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baHorN yazogabu","text_ar":"بَحْرٌ يَزْغَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sea,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"great river, that becomes"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foaming,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of commotion, and full."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","JK","S","A","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n17820","headword_ar":"زَغَبٌ","root":"zgb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Down:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yellow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"down resembling"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small hairs upon the feathers of the young bird:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small and soft hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feathers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each of these when first coming forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K:) i. e. (TA) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small and soft hair when it first appears, of a young child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a colt"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foal"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (JK, * TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"likewise of an old man, when his hair becomes thin and weak;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feathers when they first appear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the young bird:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small feathers that do not become long nor good:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Msb:) n. un. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what remains upon the head of an old man when his hair has become thin."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*ahu bizagabihi","text_ar":"اَخَذَهُ بِزَغَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took it at its commencement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its first and fresh state."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*ahu bizagabi raqabatihi","text_ar":"اَخَذَهُ بِزَغَبِ رَقَبَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took him by the down of his neck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he overtook him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","TA","Msb","JK"]},{"entry_id":"